abel pi-secondary-font\">Japanese</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">小鉄さん</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"romaji\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Rōmaji</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i>Kotetsu-san</i></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Chapter Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"volume\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Volume</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Volume_12\" title=\"Volume 12\">12</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"pages\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Pages</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">19</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"date\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Date Released</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">April 2nd, 2018</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"issue\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">WSJ Issue</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">18, 2018</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"arc\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Arc</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Swordsmith_Village_Arc\" title=\"Swordsmith Village Arc\">Swordsmith Village Arc</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Guide</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"previous\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_103\" title=\"Chapter 103\">Chapter 103</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"next\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_105\" title=\"Chapter 105\">Chapter 105</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n<nav class=\"pi-navigation pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background pi-secondary-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Chapter_104_Images\" title=\"Category:Chapter 104 Images\">Chapter 104 Images</a></nav>\n</aside>\n\n<p></p><p><b>Kotetsu</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\"><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">小</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>こ</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">鉄</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>てつ</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby>さん</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Kotetsu-san</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Installing Japanese character sets\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#198975;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is the one hundred and fourth chapter of <a href=\"/wiki/Koyoharu_Got%C5%8Dge\" title=\"Koyoharu Gotōge\">Koyoharu Gotōge's</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" title=\"Kimetsu no Yaiba (Manga)\">Kimetsu no Yaiba</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Summary\">Summary</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Kotetsu\" title=\"Kotetsu\">Kotetsu</a> proposes a variety of insults <a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro</a> could use once he becomes stronger than <a href=\"/wiki/Muichiro_Tokito\" title=\"Muichiro Tokito\">Muichiro</a>, but Tanjiro refuses the thought and tells himself he has to become stronger. He begins to train with <a href=\"/wiki/Yoriichi_Type_Zero\" title=\"Yoriichi Type Zero\">Yoriichi Type Zero</a>, with Kotetsu’s analytical skills and newfound motivation being used to excessively critique the <a href=\"/wiki/Demon_Slayer_Corps\" title=\"Demon Slayer Corps\">Demon Slayer</a>’s movements. He declares that until Tanjiro can accomplish what he wants, he won’t receive food.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 202px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/1/1b/Kotetsu_adjusts_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png/revision/latest?cb=20200323200113\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Kotetsu_adjusts_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Kotetsu_adjusts_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Kotetsu adjusts the doll by twisting its fingers.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>Kotetsu shows Tanjiro another method of adjusting the doll’s movements through twisting its fingers—such that it’d coordinate with its users’ weaknesses—and compares the actions to that of playing with a wooden puzzle box. After readjusting the doll, Tanjiro continues brutally training with it without food, water, or sleep under Kotetsu’s direction, despite the latter not understanding the limits of a human.\n</p><p>Just as Tanjiro approaches the brink of death, analogous to nearly crossing the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sanzu_River\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Sanzu River\">Sanzu River</a>, he becomes capable of smelling the incoming movement of the doll and lands a hit on it, earning him his first meal. After gaining this ability to predict movements, Tanjiro continues to train it and improves his stamina and foresight.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tright show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 182px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/4/46/A_sword%27s_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png/revision/latest?cb=20200323195228\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/A_sword's_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"279\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\"></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/4/46/A_sword%27s_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png/revision/latest?cb=20200323195228\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/4/46/A_sword%27s_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20200323195228\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"279\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"A sword&#39;s hilt emerges from Yoriichi Type Zero CH104.png\" data-image-key=\"A_sword&#39;s_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/4/46/A_sword%27s_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20200323195228\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:A_sword%27s_hilt_emerges_from_Yoriichi_Type_Zero_CH104.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">A sword's hilt emerges from Yoriichi Type Zero.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>In the middle of a spar with the doll, Tanjiro’s newly improved abilities grant him an opening to behead it, however, he hesitates mid-swing and worries about breaking the doll. Kotetsu yells at him to strike, reassuring him that he would be able to fix it. Internally, the young boy begs Tanjiro to not waver so that one day, he will become stronger than anyone else.\n</p><p>With Kotetsu's approval obtained, Tanjiro succeeds in landing a blow to the doll’s neck and breaks his training sword in the process. He apologizes to Kotetsu for the ruined sword and, after Kotetsu's sudden exclamation, Tanjiro turns to see a sword’s hilt emerging from the doll’s body where its head used to be.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Kotetsu\" title=\"Kotetsu\">Kotetsu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Muichiro_Tokito\" title=\"Muichiro Tokito\">Muichiro Tokito</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Yoriichi_Type_Zero\" title=\"Yoriichi Type Zero\">Yoriichi Type Zero</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Giyu_Tomioka\" title=\"Giyu Tomioka\">Giyu Tomioka</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Tanjiro begins training with Yoriichi Type Zero under Kotetsu's instruction.</li>\n<li>Tanjiro succeeds in landing a blow on the doll's neck, revealing a sword's hilt.</li></ul>\n\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20210108163730\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.230 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.466 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 9287/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 168185/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 77785/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 28/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  284.603      1 -total\n 72.15%  205.347      1 Template:Manga_Navigation\n 69.96%  199.100      1 Template:Navibox\n 42.27%  120.305     26 Template:Navibox/info\n 26.07%   74.210      1 Template:Chapter_Infobox\n 24.72%   70.348     26 Template:Element_List\n 20.89%   59.444     26 Template:Force_Font_Color\n  1.70%    4.832      1 Template:Nihongo\n  0.62%    1.768      2 Template:Ruby\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key prod:kimetsunoyaiba:pcache:idhash:881-0!canonical and timestamp 20210108163729 and revision id 75558\n -->\n</div>"}